channel.title: No-IP for my server isn't working? Have used it before
channel.description:
K This is like my 5th time making a server. I did Like I always do " So I think". I go to No-ip.com, register a host, something like "testing.no-ip.org". Wait a minute, run server, try to go online through the No-ip, not working, in the black box that says server is online, doesnt even show me trying to connect. Yes I have portforwarded and this has worked the last 5 times ive tried it...
Suggestions please?
